<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>TOGAPhotos 编辑精选</title>
</head>

<body
        style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f6f7f9; font-family: Segoe UI, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1f;">
<div style="width: 100%; max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 16px 12px; box-sizing: border-box;">
    <div style="width: 100%;">

        <section
                style="padding: 20px 18px; background: #ffffff; box-shadow: none; border: 0; display: block; letter-spacing: 0.01em;">
            <div style="display: block; margin-bottom: 12px;">
                <div style="display: block;">
                    <div>
                        <img src="https://cos-125-tp-cdn.794td.cn/assets/n_logo_b.jpg" alt="TOGAPhotos" width="120"
                             style="display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;">
                    </div>
                    <div style="font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 8px;">
                        入选编辑精选</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div style="height: 1px; width: 100%; background: rgba(12, 12, 13, 0.08);">
            </div>
            <div style="color: #545454; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 15px; margin-top: 10px;">
                {{username}},感谢您选择在TOGAPhotos上传您的作品。
            </div>
            <div style="display: block;">
                <article style="margin: 16px 0 0 0; padding: 20px 22px; border-left: 2px solid #2b7bff; background: #ffffff; color: #1c1c1f; box-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.05); letter-spacing: 0.01em; display: flex; flex-direction: row; justify-content: space-between; align-items: start;">
                    <div style="display: block;">
                        <div
                                style="font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #7a7a7a;">
                            图片 ID</div>
                        <div style="font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.2;">{{id}}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="display: block;">
                        <div
                                style="font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #7a7a7a;">
                图片信息</div>
                    <div
                            style="font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Menlo, monospace; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: #1c1c1f;">
                        航空公司：{{airline}}</div>
                    <div
                            style="font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Menlo, monospace; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: #1c1c1f;">
                        注册号：{{ac_reg}}</div>
                </div>
                <div
                        style="display: inline-block; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 2px 10px; border-radius: 999px; background: rgba(43, 123, 255, 0.12); color: #1a4ea2; margin-bottom: 8px;">
                    编辑精选</div>
            </article>
            </div>
            <div style="color: #545454; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 12px;">
                您的作品现已被添加至 TOGAPhotos 编辑精选合集，更多用户将有机会欣赏到您的精彩作品。感谢您对 TOGAPhotos 的支持与信任！
            </div>
            <div style="color: #545454; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 14px; text-align: right;">
                <b>TOGAPhotos 内容审核团队</b>
            </div>
            <div style="height: 1px; width: 100%; background: rgba(12, 12, 13, 0.08);">
            </div>
            <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #8a8a8a; line-height: 1.6;">
                您可以在个人设置中关闭此通知。
            </div>
            <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #8a8a8a; line-height: 1.6;">
                若您有疑问，请联系 support@togaphotos.com
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</div>
</body>

</html>